  "instructions": [
    "heat the olive oil in a hot pot vessel over medium heat.",
    "add the chopped onion and cook until softened, about 5 minutes.",
    "add the minced garlic and cook for 1 minute.",
    "add the chopped lamb and cook until browned, about 5 minutes.",
    "add the chopped rosemary, parsley, salt, and black pepper, and stir to combine.",
    "add the dried cherries and stir to combine.",
    "add the water and bring the mixture to a simmer.",
    "reduce the heat to low and cook, covered, for 1 1/2 hours, or until the lamb is tender.",
    "stir in the plain greek yogurt and cook for an additional 10 minutes.",
    "serve the tagine hot, garnished with additional chopped parsley if desired.",
    "serve with crusty bread or over couscous for a filling meal."
